{
  "id": "RAW_78f1fd1f",
  "title": "因为 AI 编程，Tailwind CSS 差点死了",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA3MzI4MjgzMw==&mid=2651011310&idx=1&sn=6b949d934d102dcb66cd31cfd9ed8760",
  "date": "2026-01-10 04:04:00",
  "author": "机器之心",
  "siteName": "机器之心",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.04259259259259259\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503523662\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=97ed75af&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW889cR13aBX42evqQIRibKlicoCrHPEpT0tQiceNphESCa2eJTqstP8G0yqMTkeMFrOGue6kOyCKdTkA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(153, 153, 153);\">编辑｜Panda</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在生成式 AI 狂飙突进的 2026 年，如果你让一个 AI 编程智能体来写网页应用，它很大概率会用到&nbsp;</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">Tailwind CSS</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">。要知道，其如今的周下载量已经超过了惊人的&nbsp;</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">2</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">6</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">00 万</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">次。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"503527523\" data-ratio=\"0.59644128113879\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1405\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=68c3e968&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gWic1JLmRXb2YuRrm3uG76sKgKibPoLibZTCYziceiabRKKxHrGMjVl3Xc9o9jZBXoJNVaw55icKQaReiaDiaw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">然而，这个备受 AI 智能体欢迎的 CSS 框架背后的团队日子却并不好过。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">前两天，Tailwind CSS 创始人 Adam Wathan 在一条 GitHub 评论中揭示了一个辛酸的现实：Tailwind 已经裁掉了&nbsp;</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">75%</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;的团队成员。这并非因为产品不再流行，恰恰相反，Tailwind 比以往任何时候都受欢迎。导致这一局面的核心原因在于，AI 带来的巨大流量与商业转化彻底脱钩：</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">AI 在写代码，就没有人类会去访问文档，也就没人为他们的付费产品买单</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">整体来说：</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">流量下降 40%，收入损失 80%。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5321983715766099\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1351\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503527525\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=111c1e35&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gWic1JLmRXb2YuRrm3uG76sKgsPwnAYAwKGeoltsARregZzSG7MIrHy3dAxzrMXmXCrQuWE4jkwViaLg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\">注：本截图以及以下多张截图原本是英文，由机器翻译为中文</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">这一事件撕开了 AI 时代开源软件商业模式最隐秘也最痛楚的一角。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">「我们没时间做不能维持生计的事」</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">危机的爆发源于一个看似普通的 Pull Request。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">2025 年 11 月，一位用户 quantizor 希望新增一个 llms.txt 接口，用于向大模型提供经过优化的项目文档内容，方便 LLM 更好地理解和使用该项目。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5202354672553348\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1359\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503527524\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=008e78e1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gWic1JLmRXb2YuRrm3uG76sKgsVabyrqK77qlS5iatIssa7j1wZcM0l0TpEEs9vDRS4cyfdX7DTgUODg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\"><a href=\"https://github.com/tailwindlabs/tailwindcss.com/pull/2388\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/tailwindlabs/tailwindcss.com/pull/2388</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">然而，该 Pull Request 并未被即时处理，而是被搁置了一个多月，便有用户发起了评论问询。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">这时候，Adam Wathan 现身解答了疑惑，并表示 Tailwind 公司已经陷入了财务困境，而让 LLM 更容易阅读文档会让问题更加严重。Tailwind 的商业模式依赖于开发者访问官方文档，进而在页面上接触到他们的付费产品（如 UI 组件库 Tailwind UI）。然而，随着 Cursor 等 AI 编程工具的普及，开发者不再需要查阅文档，AI 可以直接生成代码。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.2631970260223048\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1345\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503527527\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=177cc063&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gWic1JLmRXb2YuRrm3uG76sKgzuMXguNDIqWZ4t7IZaZM52VIK4thsx9ictou144rrEEW283dUAqXh5A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Wathan 的评论引发了更多讨论，这也让他有机会进一步解释其公司面临的困难：他们</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">刚刚在前一天裁掉了 75% 的工程团队</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">，而原因是「AI 对我们业务造成了极其残酷的冲击」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Wathan 写道：「尽管 Tailwind 比以往任何时候都更受欢迎，但与 2023 年初相比，我们文档的访问量下降了大约&nbsp;</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">40%</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">。文档是人们了解我们商业产品的唯一途径，没有客户，我们就无法负担维护这个框架的成本。」更具体而言：「Tailwind 的增长速度比以往任何时候都快，规模也比以往任何时候都大，但我们的收入却下降了将近&nbsp;</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">80%</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">。」</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">他还在这条评论中表达了担忧：「这个项目在没有人再受雇来维护它的情况下，最终只会变成一个无人维护、被遗弃的软件。」</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">最终，为了生存，他拒绝了那个让 AI 更方便「白嫖」知识的请求，关闭了这个 Pull Request。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">开源项目的商业模式</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在这里，我们看到了 AI 编程智能体大爆发时代的另一面。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">这一事件自然引发了网友的高度关注和争议。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">有开发者直言不讳地在下面评论说 Wathan 拒绝这个 Pull Request 并将其归因于 AI 的做法是错的，他表示：「这件事唯一应该受到指责的人是 Tailwind 的 CEO / 主要维护者。他们做出了错误的决定，雇佣了程序员却不知道如何才能赚到足够的钱来支付他们的工资。」</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.43131462333825704\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1354\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503527528\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d6c5133a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gWic1JLmRXb2YuRrm3uG76sKgicmvc40iaiadtXbUACfXLQOxVibtEllkib3rTMlZNpwhjro17tEA9rE4nmw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">甚至还有人恶语相向。最后，Wathan 选择了锁帖。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.21420118343195266\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"845\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503527526\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=71fc93ee&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gWic1JLmRXb2YuRrm3uG76sKg20EzmhcdTMiaibffMKSXXuNA18e5MwVpNASROCj0xsv5rGSCOys5NY0Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">但事件并未就此平息，只是转移了位置，其中很多讨论都围绕着</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">开源项目的商业模式</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在 X 上，技术作家 Bilgin Ibryam 评论说：「这并非技术失败，而是商业模式的失败。」</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.332470892626132\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"773\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503527530\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=aeac40fd&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gWic1JLmRXb2YuRrm3uG76sKgbt0LtubL4sgI3iamnAM89JBEB9vuDBbMNIsicj0OicG6iaGqiaAficgbGiboQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在过去，开源软件通过「免费软件 + 付费服务/托管」的模式生存。而在 Web 开发领域，像 Tailwind 这样的项目，其商业通常闭环是：</span></span></p>\n  <ol style=\"list-style-type: decimal;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li style=\"font-size: 15px;\">\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">工具开源</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">：吸引海量开发者使用</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li style=\"font-size: 15px;\">\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">文档引流</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">：开发者为了查阅用法访问官网</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li style=\"font-size: 15px;\">\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">转化变现</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">：在官网展示高质量的付费模版和组件库</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ol>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">但在 2026 年，AI 成了用户。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">正如 Ibryam 所言，AI 在不知不觉中使用了开源项目，但 AI 从不访问网站，从不看广告，更不可能掏出信用卡购买一套 UI 组件包。对于 AI 而言，文档只是训练数据，而非消费入口。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">当中间的文档引流环节被 AI 截断，后端的商业转化自然归零。Tailwind 实际上变成了一个为 AI 及其背后的巨头免费提供基础设施，却无法从中获取任何价值的「假奶牛」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">下面展示了更多网友讨论：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.2857142857142857\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"791\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503527529\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=efedf9ea&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gWic1JLmRXb2YuRrm3uG76sKgpcf0ALjPUIkkQX86PM3HgtTJ2Cib4OFIezJe9sXiasdqIvHU6ibby8O7A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.30828025477707005\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"785\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503527531\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=bf8d523a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gWic1JLmRXb2YuRrm3uG76sKgMDw4c0nD7W0icWibfkRgOJK0ibGhmwwwibSfx5MT3DtgAz2Cx3OiafD4NMg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.21546261089987326\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"789\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503527532\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=297a0f06&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gWic1JLmRXb2YuRrm3uG76sKgoLLGUM2QGq7ABSCibgS3OkHUaonSIBsGbsERkjqLBdRr1vLVBRBic1Qg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.516497461928934\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"788\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503527533\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=36287b93&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gWic1JLmRXb2YuRrm3uG76sKgpCQNJliaqCUWdCic9wXiaX85KtZ7UySfQagiaNh6sQJayxpdVjJzs4YIpA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">还有一些人分享了自己的点子，试图帮助 Tailwind 渡过难关：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5734355044699873\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"783\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503527534\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7494d52b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gWic1JLmRXb2YuRrm3uG76sKgUwrFU62eCib0SF6YfsaPS24iboXhAXN4XA8llRa9nuxEJx0jUPzBQuFA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.47715736040609136\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"788\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503527536\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=76662c2c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gWic1JLmRXb2YuRrm3uG76sKgotAxavANZKZiaFbP7Jyvkkock8hE94Zt4hw3OgAzmGgMIGibWkwIvXNA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">也有人觉得 Wathan 的言语过于夸张，说是裁掉了 75% 的人，其实是裁掉了 4 人中的 3 人。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3729096989966555\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"598\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503527535\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6213131f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gWic1JLmRXb2YuRrm3uG76sKgmeTESDqZo2nnbqP3q5iacTg0akM5X0wia11dN8KnI36zY2ibknqibRaibvQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">但也有网友对 Tailwind 的遭遇表达了同情和关切：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.2987179487179487\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"780\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503527537\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=8b8298fc&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gWic1JLmRXb2YuRrm3uG76sKgTx9ckibC7hxaB5OdEY5JnVczcjZOnVd1flFkMxQbZI0dZice38v64Cyg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4844903988183161\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"677\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503527538\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d674371b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gWic1JLmRXb2YuRrm3uG76sKgBcWVOKb9C7E4AynCUzia6Kor8EXtGRaIQQticy1sMYgTlnoyayXc02dQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">多家公司伸出援手</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">这个故事略显悲伤，但却有一个还算不错的暂时结局：Tailwind 的呼救被听到了，谷歌等多家公司伸出了援手。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">前天，Adam Wathan 就已经在 X 上晒出了一份赞助者名单，其中可以看到 Cursor、Shopify、CodeRabbit 等多家知名 AI 和科技公司。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.217005076142132\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"788\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503527539\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7d0fb780&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gWic1JLmRXb2YuRrm3uG76sKgq7szoQXgkngibdYDX3kxe0PH6V1qONPyz0Lyic3IPOzhceoS89RjqibgQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">而各档位的赞助金额如下：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6200626959247649\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1595\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503527540\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=1f895d83&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gWic1JLmRXb2YuRrm3uG76sKgOk4NFwnwCcK6c2HunibYG7t2MyQUViayDtVWfFVuRKgkywnpibvXt8iaVA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">9 号上午，谷歌 AI Studio 产品负责人 Logan Kilpatrick 也宣布了赞助 Tailwind 项目（每年 5000 美元的 Partner 档位）。对于像谷歌和 Cursor 这样直接受益于高质量 AI 编程体验的公司来说，确保 Tailwind 继续维护显然符合他们的利益。毕竟，如果底层框架死了，AI 生成的代码质量也会随之下降。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3059125964010283\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"778\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503527541\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e57b41f1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gWic1JLmRXb2YuRrm3uG76sKgeL5YHgrsreBqvPozlRVIJwiahnGTfThWk31aTBmxy8RbyJv6bysMpNg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">此外，该公司前些天推出的每年 120 美元的个人订阅服务「Tailwind Insider」也已经收获了更多新客户。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.12197743148844707\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1861\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503527542\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=62347297&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gWic1JLmRXb2YuRrm3uG76sKgofCjd9ym87l0FmnDCVXeDGw7ou9aPYaE84UexrgTRwFEJEWKxxWqzA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">这些赞助和收入应该可以缓解该公司的燃眉之急。至于被裁掉的工程师，也有可能会被重新招募回来。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.45790816326530615\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"784\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503527543\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=195d0fe3&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gWic1JLmRXb2YuRrm3uG76sKg8Z5KDoVp8fiatCdUicxorcibsChoZVSTqyMYGo5Kgfggv9H7do6Np0iadA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">但这也并不是一个十分完美的结局，Tailwind 还是需要自己努力寻找合适的商业模式，正如 Wathan 所言，这些支持让公司感到「很安心」，他们不需要被拯救，而是获得了一些喘息的时间来探索新的方向。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7936305732484077\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"785\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503527544\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=38e66863&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gWic1JLmRXb2YuRrm3uG76sKgB5OucGicKL0W5A7JUO2AE8sLFQxgaMjOKv96I1sW9Ko3rH7mZmo8Gkg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">又或者等待被某家大公司收购？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.9886075949367089\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"790\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503527545\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=817dbd50&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gWic1JLmRXb2YuRrm3uG76sKgUasAYaKzzedTJjlKicgiaDqGLuKlcl8SBWDHXVLDiaRFPt7WV6sxaXOEw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">警钟为谁而鸣</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Tailwind 的故事有了一个暂时温暖的结局，但它留给行业的思考却是有些寒冷的。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">当 AI 能够完美地消化信息、生成代码、甚至替代交互时，所有依附于「人类注意力」和「人类访问量」的商业逻辑都面临着重构的风险。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">对于开源维护者而言，2026 年的新课题已经摆在桌面上：当你的用户变成不知疲倦且一毛不拔的 AI 时，你该向谁收费？</span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "AI 编程智能体的普及导致开源项目 Tailwind CSS 流量骤降和收入锐减，迫使其裁员并重新审视开源商业模式，引发了对 AI 时代开源项目盈利模式的深刻思考。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "AI 编程智能体的普及导致开源项目 Tailwind CSS 流量骤降和收入锐减，迫使其裁员并重新审视开源商业模式，引发了对 AI 时代开源项目盈利模式的深刻思考。",
  "summary": "文章深入探讨了在 AI 编程智能体兴起的背景下，广受欢迎的 CSS 框架 Tailwind CSS 所面临的商业困境。由于 AI 大量使用其文档生成代码，导致 Tailwind 的官网流量和付费产品转化率急剧下降，创始人 Adam Wathan 透露团队裁员 75%，收入骤降 80%。这一事件揭示了开源项目依赖“免费软件+付费服务/托管”模式在 AI 时代面临的挑战，即 AI 成为用户但无法产生商业价值，导致开源项目的商业闭环被截断。文章还讨论了社区对此事件的争议、同情，以及谷歌、Cursor 等公司伸出援手提供赞助，缓解了 Tailwind 的燃眉之急。但文章指出，这并非长久之计，开源项目需要重新思考在 AI 时代如何建立可持续的商业模式。",
